Name: Saber
Desc: The solitary Heroic Spirit traverses the long night of fate. The banner of the round table remains unfurled in a dream. Alas, the knight-king of Camelot has yet to reach that ever-distant utopia.\nThough still a young maiden, she has heeded the call for this most unique iteration of the Holy Grail War. With the Sword in the Stone offering its choice once more, how shall she shatter the illusions of the past?\n"The wishes I did not fulfil will end here."

1.Name: The Lost White Walls
1.Desc: Increases DMG dealt by <unbreak>Saber</unbreak> by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. After <unbreak>Saber</unbreak> uses a Basic ATK or Skill, additionally gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> "Core Resonance."

2.Name: The Sealed Round Table
2.Desc: Increases CRIT DMG dealt with "Release, the Golden Scepter" and "Strike Air: Hammer of the Wind King" by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. For every 1 "Core Resonance" gained, additionally increases CRIT DMG dealt by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>. This effect can be stacked up to <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> time(s).

3.Name: The Fabled Fifteen Centuries
3.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

4.Name: The Wondrous Fourteen Nights
4.Desc: Increases <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> Wind <u>RES PEN</u> by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. After using Ultimate, increases <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> Wind <u>RES PEN</u> by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>, stacking up to <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> time(s).

5.Name: The Dreamed Utopian Dawn
5.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

6.Name: The Long Fated Night
6.Desc: Increases the <u>RES PEN</u> caused by <unbreak>Saber's </unbreak> Ultimate DMG by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. Upon entering battle and using the Ultimate for the first time, regenerates a fixed <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> Energy for <unbreak>Saber</unbreak>. After an Ultimate is used <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> time(s), this effect can be triggered once more.

101401.Name: Invisible Air: Barrier of the Wind King
101401.Desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to one designated enemy.

101402.Name: Strike Air: Hammer of the Wind King
101402.Desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to one designated enemy, and deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to enemies adjacent to it. If currently holding "Core Resonance," and consuming it after this Skill usage would fully regenerate <unbreak>Saber</unbreak>'s Energy, then increases the DMG multiplier for this usage of Skill. Each "Core Resonance" increases the DMG multiplier for this usage of Skill by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#4[i]%</unbreak></color>, then immediately consumes all "Core Resonance" to fully regenerate Energy for <unbreak>Saber</unbreak>. Otherwise, immediately gains <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> "Core Resonance."

101403.Name: Excalibur
101403.Desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to all enemies. Then, deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to one random enemy, occurring <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> time(s). After using Ultimate, the next Basic ATK switches to "Release, the Golden Scepter," and only "Release, the Golden Scepter" can be used.

101404.Name: Dragon Reactor Core
101404.Desc: Obtains <unbreak>#8[i]</unbreak> "Core Resonance" point(s) when entering battle. When any ally target uses an Ultimate, increases DMG dealt by <unbreak>Saber</unbreak> by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turn(s) and obtains <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> "Core Resonance" point(s). Consuming 1 "Core Resonance" point will regenerate a fixed <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> Energy for <unbreak>Saber</unbreak>.

101406.Name: Attack
101406.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

101407.Name: Behold, the King of Knights
101407.Desc: After using Technique, increases <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s) and grants <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> "Core Resonance" at the start of the next battle.

101408.Name: Release, the Golden Scepter
101408.Desc: Gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> "Core Resonance" and deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to all enemies. If there are 2/1 enemy(ies) on the field, additionally deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color>/<color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#4[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> ATK to all enemies.

1.PointDesc: Increases <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> CRIT Rate by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. When entering battle and using an Enhanced Basic ATK, obtains "Mana Burst." If <unbreak>Saber</unbreak> has "Mana Burst" and "Core Resonance" at the same time, then she can fully regenerate her Energy after using a Skill and consumes "Mana Burst" to allow allies to recover 1 Skill Point while letting her immediately take action.

<unbreak>Saber</unbreak> can accumulate up to <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> excess Energy. After using Ultimate, the excess Energy is cleared and a corresponding amount is regenerated. When the battle starts, if Energy is below <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak>, it is regenerated to <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.
When using Skill, increases <unbreak>Saber's</unbreak> CRIT DMG by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turns.
